<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 Apr 2022 06:07:17 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Benz EQV 首款電動 MPV 七人車，續航力 378 公里 + 配 EQ 專屬 MBUX 系統</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/12/benzneweqvmpv/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=benzneweqvmpv</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 12 Apr 2022 06:07:17 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1095258</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Mercedes-Benz 將在本月 14 日推出全新的 EQV 300 七座 MPV，主打高續航力、快速充電 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Mercedes-Benz 將在本月 14 日推出全新的 EQV 300 七座 MPV，主打高續航力、快速充電、提供 EQ 專屬的 MBUX 智能操作，屬於私人、商務通用的多功能七人車。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">EQV 300 提供兩款型號，分別為長軸距（3,200 毫米）的 EQV 300 Long，定價低於港幣 HK$1,200,000；</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095268" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/long-694x405.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="405" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/long-694x405.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/long-768x449.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/long.jpg 1039w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">以及特長軸距（3,430 毫米）的 EQV 300 Extra Long，定價低於港幣 HK$1,000,000。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095269" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/extra-long-694x421.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="421" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/extra-long-694x421.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/extra-long-768x466.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/extra-long.jpg 1046w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">新車與 V-Class 相同，量產版本於西班牙北部 Vitoria 生產。車上電池可用容量達 90kWh，提供 378 km 的續航力 (WLTP)。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">EQV 300 在行駛時也會將動力回收為電能。當加速或制動時,會將動能轉化為電能，為高壓電池充電。駕駛者可透過撥動軚盤後方左、右的撥片，增強或減少回收幅度。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_128-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">最低迴收幅度時,車輛會仿如滑行；而最高幅度時,駕駛者基本可單踏板操，在大部份情況下，動力回收時的減速力已足夠取代制動系統。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095270" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-694x472.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-694x472.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-1280x870.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-768x522.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-1536x1044.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-2048x1392.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0436_006-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">新車亦配備 DAuto 回收模式，自動啟動的 ECO Assistant 可協助駕駛者取得最佳節能效果。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;"> EQV 300 同時配備車內水冷式交流電充電器，最高功率為 11 kW，方便在家或公眾充電站作交流電充電。EQV 在透過直流快速充電站以 110 kW 的功率充電時， 只需約 45 分鐘便可由 10% 充電至 80%。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095267" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image002-694x361.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="361" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image002-694x361.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image002-768x399.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image002.jpg 816w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">EQV 300 將電能動力系統（eATS）放於流線型的車頭，前泵把設有充電插座，將電動摩打、固定齒比傳動系統、冷卻系統和電力總成藏於車頭內。其摩打輸出高達 204 hp。 </span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0247_002-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">其鋰電池組擺放在車底並置中，確保良好的操控表現。同時令 EQV 300 地臺平坦，車廂空間靈活多變，適合各種用途。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095264" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-694x455.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-694x455.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-1280x839.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-768x503.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1-1536x1007.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-1280x836.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-768x502.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2-1536x1003.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/seat-2.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">如作為家庭 MPV 時，乘客可使用中排豪華獨立座椅，第三排座椅更可作多種編排，方便出行。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095259" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Luxury-seats-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">因應 Mercedes-EQ 而更新的 MBUX 系統亦是另一重點。在 10 吋高解像屏幕，EQ 頁面可提供多項顯示，如有關充電量、能量流和耗電量的圖像。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_513-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">屏幕亦可控制導航系統及駕駛模式。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon-768x509.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon.jpg 1032w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">MBUX 系統的一大強項是以「Hey Mercedes」關鍵詞啟動的智能語音操作，支援多項資訊娛樂，如輸入目的地、撥打電話、選擇歌曲、聽取短訊、控制空氣調節、燈光系統等。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095271" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon2-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon2-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon2-768x454.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/mon2.jpg 1087w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在外形上，EQV 300 亦貫徹品牌旗下 EQ 家族的設計語言。EQV 車頭鬼面罩採用 Black </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Panel 設計，配以鍍鉻飾條，車側配上 17 吋的輕合金輪圈。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1095272" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-1280x703.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-768x422.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-1536x843.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-2048x1124.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/20C0433_073-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Mercedes Benz 將在本月 14 日正式在香港展出 EQV 300，有興趣的讀者可到其<a href="https://www.mercedes-benz.com.hk/zh_HK/passengercars/mercedes-benz-cars/models/eqv/explore.html">官網</a>查看更多。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：Mercedes-Benz</p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
